{"tid":2423668,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】10歲男童染疫引起併發症截四肢保命 媽媽：他崩潰痛哭","createTime":"2021-02-26T04:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T06:24:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8901e3d78b9ff877005abb67275f1ac1fb3d5000","tid":2423668,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:56:52.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續，美國一名10歲男童確診武漢肺炎後，出現罕見併發症「小兒多系統發炎症候群」（MIS-C），影響身體凝血功能，被迫截四肢保命。其母在眾籌平台GoFundMe分享兒子接受治療的過程，並希望籌款做更進一步治療。<br />\n<br />\n10歲男童Dae&rsquo;Shun Jamison於去年12月20日起感到劇烈頭痛，隔日因高燒入院，後來確診。確診後醫生發現他患有併發症「小兒多系統發炎症候群」（MIS-C），導致身體不同部位有發炎症狀，另影響血液凝固功能。<br />\n<br />\nDae&rsquo;Shun曾要戴呼吸機，出現心臟衰竭，其他器官逐漸失去功能等問題，需要做靜脈透析及使用ECMO體外膜肺氧合機器替代心肺，將氧氣注入他的血液。不過，由於Dae&rsquo;Shun有血液凝固問題，四肢缺乏血液流動和手部組織受損，故要截肢保命。<br />\n&quot;他右手動脈中有血塊，並已超過2星期，所使用的血液稀釋劑也無效。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n於是醫生決定為他先後切除右腿、雙手及左腿。<br />\n<br />\nDae&rsquo;Shun的媽媽表示，起初兒子因患有自閉症的關係，對於截肢、靜脈透析等都不理解。但後來，當醫護人員和自己向他解釋翌日要截除雙腿時，他明白了。他明白手術醒來後，雙腿會變得不一樣。<br />\n&quot;他完全崩潰痛哭了。我無法想像我的孩子會發生這種事。請大家繼續為我們祈禱。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n媽媽表示，未能想像兒子日後怎樣生活。兒子很喜歡踢足球，希望日後他能適應用假肢，再次行走。<br />\n<br />\nHelen DeVos Children&rsquo;s Hospital兒童傳染科主任 Rosemary Olivero 指，通常兒童感染新冠肺炎都是輕症，因此很難讓家長及早發現MIS-C症狀。MIS-C症狀通常在感染新冠肺炎後幾周出現，臨床症狀類似川崎氏症，會造成皮疹、結膜炎、腹瀉等。部分嚴重MIS-C患者會出現心臟功能障礙，加上血液凝塊或出血問題，影響身體其他部位輸送血液。<br />\n<br />\n她提醒，家長應密切監測兒童的健康狀況，發現疑似症狀立即求醫。因為往往兒童染疫後病徵輕微，而忽略引發罕見併發症風險。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2885000/2887290/blood_thumb_20210226_J_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2885000%2F2887290%2Fblood_thumb_20210226_J_1024.jpg&h=fbaa876f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2885000/2887290/53607088_1609288246978867_r_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2885000%2F2887290%2F53607088_1609288246978867_r_1024.jpeg&h=c64f16bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38023279608e23d96656447860a0910c8fd9385d","tid":2423668,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6a533f351b982d2b9abe2d32d74794ea55f5f0","tid":2423668,"uid":36383,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:59:30.000Z","msg":"Black Life Matters"},{"pid":"a3a8208d6f86f2a4970afc8a012be9e39c45ed08","tid":2423668,"uid":364851,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:04:31.000Z","msg":"黑色nick vujicic"},{"pid":"71c8db2484d09b4076932856b2a5338b83160a12","tid":2423668,"uid":288437,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:06:44.000Z","msg":"叫BLM養<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c4441b6e5f6f6a867676f1791d77557020e0be","tid":2423668,"uid":156913,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://mechanicalanimereviews.files.wordpress.com/2020/11/gundam-thunderbolt-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmechanicalanimereviews.files.wordpress.com%2F2020%2F11%2Fgundam-thunderbolt-1.jpg&h=57524e60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8fa8aa6b10be1733cf029b3316205c1773ed228","tid":2423668,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:11:55.000Z","msg":"睇錯染髮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c395b5c415c071cc002fde5d900ba28078460c","tid":2423668,"uid":65091,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:11:58.000Z","msg":"慘 呢世都冇得用指紋unlock部iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03de